data.description: Welcome to this fully updated half duplex just two blocks from Wash Park! This 3-bed, 2-bath gem seamlessly combines 1923 charm with modern amenities. The open main floor features an eat-in kitchen, formal dining space, and a living room with the original fireplace. Fresh paint, updated fixtures, new quartz countertops, and subway tile backsplash in the kitchen make the space move-in ready. Use the front room as an office or guest space. A 3/4 bath on the main level is well-sized and adjacent to the second main-floor bedroom. The original sun porch has been fully integrated into the home and offers a great bonus space in which to relax or work out. Downstairs, the private primary suite boasts a full bath, laundry access, and plenty of storage. Outside, enjoy the fully fenced backyard with access to the shared detached garage. Welcome home to effortless living in the heart of Wash Park!
